


;; define the file structure you would like

;; comments begin with ;;
;; directories end with /
;; white space is important in structure definition
;; variables are enclosed within % % 
;; app_name is the 2nd parameter given during ignite invocation

;; here's an example:


%app_name%/
  some_directory/
    some_file.rb


;; in the above example make sure that a file called some_file.rb is in the templates directory of _this_ folder

